{"tid":1667272,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"721唔見人，講緊你地呀，快Ｄ出黎黨鐵站","createTime":"2019-10-21T11:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T11:38:28.000Z","uid":65790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"afd0046867a6a9935bd9f78112a382ad23c08fe4","tid":1667272,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjXp25L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjXp25L.jpg&h=730245c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n10.21 全港黨鐵站靜坐<br />\n7時21分默站一分鐘<br />\n麻煩短時間內極速SHARE<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">荃灣線</span>︰荃灣、深水埗、旺角、尖沙咀<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">觀塘線</span>︰九龍塘、黃大仙、九龍灣、觀塘<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">港島線</span>︰金鐘、銅鑼灣、太古<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">東涌線</span>︰東涌<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">西鐵</span>︰屯門、天水圍<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">東鐵</span>︰大圍、大埔墟<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">南港島線</span>︰<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黃竹坑</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">馬鞍山線</span>︰馬鞍山<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">將軍澳線</span>︰將軍澳"},{"pid":"f518e8ed113788b8cb65a5d7447203f0a7d70312","tid":1667272,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:22:16.000Z","msg":"唔見人"},{"pid":"ccf9ade75483d587131bb9bc070b420d4af3fcd6","tid":1667272,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:23:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f23277d87a20b6020c13474d69329f7978762eba","tid":1667272,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:24:09.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"1ff1b223c968949c120f728749344ca8dbadeab5","tid":1667272,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:24:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"30d59983c4bf8bb62b2be57acab9dfe72fd81811","tid":1667272,"uid":157069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"449a6f50976d3c3b1800a03e1785aef46c981f8c","tid":1667272,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85486c99bff79cff789bacd7a1c2adff017c5506","tid":1667272,"uid":5264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:25:47.000Z","msg":"重點係有錢都買唔撚到"},{"pid":"1c7c7f2fdfc597b25b70b0bed46a1a93cb964c3e","tid":1667272,"uid":19566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:26:30.000Z","msg":"外面冇宣傳<br />\n點會有人出啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3802e72bf18266d36b09b10b5fcf33f4095f8408","tid":1667272,"uid":157069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af7e9b6ca30e73c5d3a284e25e8301a026654b3e","tid":1667272,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c31aa0dd4a7bf9298a87ab26583c28ff055246","tid":1667272,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:35:13.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"dd310d81c51279f58af244648e67d3321933c5be","tid":1667272,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:38:28.000Z","msg":"推"}]}